    <div class="pageBreak"><h1>Informed Consent of Participation</h1>
        <p>You are invited to participate in the {{type}} <b>{{title}}</b>, initiated and conducted by {{#each researchers}}{{../prefix}}{{name}}{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}{{#if @last}}, and {{/if}}{{/each}}{{thePIname}}. The
            research is supervised by {{thePIname}} at {{institution}}{{#if (unequal departmentHead thePIname)}} under {{departmentHead}}{{/if}}.
            {{#if funding}}This study is funded and financed by the research project {{funding}}.{{/if}}
            Please note:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your participation is voluntary.</li>
            <li>The {{type}} will last approximately {{duration}}.</li>
            {{#if record.demographics}}<li>We will record personal demographics ({{personalData}}).</li>{{/if}}
            {{#if record.photos}}<li>We will take photos during the session.</li>{{/if}}
            {{#if record.videos}}<li>We will record videos during the session.</li>{{/if}}
            {{#if record.audio}}<li>We will record audio during the session.</li>{{/if}}
            {{#if record.motion}}<li>We will track your body motion during the session.</li>{{/if}}
            {{#if record.eyetracking}}<li>We will track your eye and head motion during the session.</li>{{/if}}
            {{#if record.physiological}}<li>We will take physiological measurements of your body.</li>{{/if}}
            {{#if record.screenrecording}}<li>We will record the screen on your device that are necessary for the study.</li>{{/if}}
            {{#if record.interaction}}<li>We will record interaction data (e.g., clicks, timings) during the session.</li>{{/if}}
            {{#if (equal compensation 'points')}}<li>You will receive 1 credit point per hour for your study course as compensation.</li>
            {{else if (equal compensation 'moneyPoints')}}<li>You will receive 1 credit point per hour for your study course as compensation or {{monetaryCompensation}} as monetary compensation.</li>
            {{else if (equal compensation 'money')}}<li>You will receive {{monetaryCompensation}} as compensation.</li>
            {{else}}<li>You will receive no compensation.</li>{{/if}}
            <li>We may publish results from this and other sessions.</li>
            {{#if (equal share 'yes')}}<li>All data you provide in this {{type}} will be published <b>not anonymized</b></li>.
            {{else if (equal share 'anonymized')}}<li>All data you provide in this field study will be published anonymized; thus, they will neither include your name nor cannot be associated with your identity.</li>
            {{else}}<li>The data collected cannot be viewed or used for further research by anyone outside the researchers involved in this work. </li>{{/if}}
        </ul>
        <p>If you have any questions about the whole informed consent process of this research or your rights as a
            human research subject, please contact
            {{#if ethicalComittee}}
                our ethics committee office: {{ethicalComittee}}.
            {{else}}
                {{#if departmentHead}}
                    {{thePIname}} (E-Mail: {{thePIemail}}) or {{departmentHead}}.
                {{else}}
                    {{thePIname}} (E-Mail: {{thePIemail}}).
                {{/if}}
            {{/if}}

            You should carefully read the settings below. You may take as much time as you need to read the consent
            form. If you do not fully agree with something, or if your questions have not all been answered to your
            satisfaction, then you should not give your consent. </p>
