            your confidentiality as a participant in this {{type}} will remain secure.
            {{#if (equal encryption 'true')}}All the data you provide in this {{type}} will be encrypted. {{/if}}
            Data collected in this {{type}} will be treated in compliance with the GDPR. </p>
