                manner that they can no longer be traced back to your person or only with disproportionate technical
                effort. Despite these measures, we cannot guarantee the anonymity of your personal data.
            {{else}}
                All data you provide in this {{type}} will not be published and kept confidential.
            {{/if}}

            {{#if (equal type 'interview')}}
                {{#if (unequal share 'yes')}}
                        The interview transcript will be primarily analyzed by {{#if thePIname}}{{thePIname}}{{/if}}{{#if secondResearcherName}}{{#if thePIname}} and{{/if}} {{secondResearcherName}}{{/if}}{{#if thirdResearcherName}}{{#if secondResearcherName}} and{{/if}} {{thirdResearcherName}}{{/if}}.
