            {{else}}
                Data collected that have not been made public will be deleted after the end of the research.
            {{/if}}
        </p>
        <p>As with any publication or online-related activity, the risk of a breach of confidentiality is always
            possible. According to the GDPR, the researchers will inform the participant if a breach of confidential
            data is detected. </p></div>
